service: start-ec2-instance

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: us-east-1
  environment:
    EC2_INSTANCE_ID: ${env:EC2_INSTANCE_ID}

functions:
  startInstance:
    handler: index.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /start-instance
          method: get
          cors: true
    iamRoleStatements:
      - Effect: Allow
        Action:
          - ec2:DescribeInstances
          - ec2:StartInstances
        Resource: "*"

plugins:
  - serverless-dotenv-plugin
